-- Syngenta, Bayer CropScience Sign Sign Licensing Pact for Insect Control
-- Simone Meier
-- 2010-07-14T05:03:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/syngenta-bayer-cropscience-sign-sign-licensing-pact-for-insect-control.html

          
          
             Syngenta AG said it entered an
agreement with Bayer CropScience for a worldwide, non-exclusive
license for use of instect control technology in cotton,
according to a statement on its website today.  
          
          


  


        